text: Stephen Clissold (17 February 1825 - 26 May 1898) was an English cricketer. He played eight first-class matches for Cambridge University Cricket Club between 1844 and 1848. ==See also== * List of Cambridge University Cricket Club players ==References== ==External links== * Category:1825 births Category:1898 deaths Category:English cricketers Category:Cambridge University cricketers Category:Cricketers from Greater London Category:Marylebone Cricket Club cricketers
